longBusinessSummary: Mandarin Oriental International Limited owns and operates hotels, resorts, and residences in Asia, Europe, the Middle East, Africa, and the Americas. It is also involved in the hotel and residences branding and management; and property development activities. The company was founded in 1963 and is based in Quarry Bay, Hong Kong. Mandarin Oriental International Limited is a subsidiary of Jardine Strategic Limited.
